    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This +1 heavy steel shield bears the symbol of Gorum, the Lord in Iron, on its face. In the hands of a character with the challengeAPG class feature, this shield grants additional abilities. By spending one use of her challenge class feature as an immediate action, the wearer of a challenging shield can apply her Charisma bonus to her shield bonus to AC against a target of her challenge for 1 minute.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +1 heavy steel shield</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, nereid's grace (Pathfinder RPG Advanced Race Guide 179)</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Armor Masters Handbook",
